     I don't think it compares. It drags &amp; is longer than it needs to be. The only reason I finished it was for the happy ending. Could have just read the<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
     I don't think it compares. It drags &amp; is longer than it needs to be. The only reason I finished it was for the happy ending. Could have just read the last chapter &amp; got the conclusion to Wind I think readers are seeking.<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
